      <title>美联储降息预期推动股市上涨；美元企稳：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-22/asian-stocks-eye-cautious-gains-as-us-worries-ease-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亚洲股市从上周的抛售中反弹，因美国通胀温和，重燃美联储降息预期。美元回落后企稳。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-22/asian-stocks-eye-cautious-gains-as-us-worries-ease-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 22 Dec 2024 22:35:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>自特朗普胜选以来，比特币首次出现周跌幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-22/bitcoin-btc-faces-worst-week-since-trump-win-as-fed-outlook-bites</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美联储谨慎的政策前景削弱了人们对当选总统对加密货币行业的乐观情绪，比特币自唐纳德·特朗普赢得大选以来首次出现周度下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-22/bitcoin-btc-faces-worst-week-since-trump-win-as-fed-outlook-bites</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 22 Dec 2024 20:23:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>一架小型飞机坠毁巴西城市，造成 10 人死亡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-22/small-plane-crashes-into-brazilian-city-hitting-populated-area</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据当地政府称，一架小型飞机在巴西南部南里奥格兰德州格拉玛多市坠毁。该州州长爱德华多·莱特在 X 上的一篇帖子中表示，事故造成 10 人死亡，全部为乘客，地面上有 17 人受伤。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-22/small-plane-crashes-into-brazilian-city-hitting-populated-area</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 22 Dec 2024 17:31:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
